page_title: 'Quickstart: Use Azure OpenAI Assistants (Preview) via the Azure OpenAI Studio'
page_description: Walkthrough on how to get started with Azure OpenAI and make your first completions call with Azure OpenAI Studio.
chunk_content: Prerequisites- An Azure subscription - Create one for free.- An Azure OpenAI resource with a compatible model in a supported region.- We recommend reviewing the Responsible AI transparency note and other Responsible AI resources to familiarize yourself with the capabilities and limitations of the Azure OpenAI Service.
